query:
SELECT e.id, e.title, e.trailId, e.guideId, t.name as trailName, u.name as guideName 
FROM expeditions e 
LEFT JOIN trails t ON e.trailId = t.id 
LEFT JOIN users u ON e.guideId = u.id;
